cite-empty-state-copy.en: Cite your references in a click. You can start by importing your references or by adding references manually.

figure-cite-empty-state-copy.en: Cite your figures in a click. Get all your cross-references in correct format and order. You can start by adding figures using the “Insert” option in the toolbar.

figure-cite-empty-state-copy2.en: Once created, your figures appear here as a list, which you can then cite easily.

formula-cite-empty-state-copy.en: Add formulae or equations using the 'Insert' menu and they will be available to cite here.

table-wrap-cite-empty-state-copy.en: Cite your tables in a click. Get all your cross-references in correct format and order. You can start by creating tables using the “Insert” option in the toolbar.

table-wrap-cite-empty-state-copy2.en: Once created, your tables appear here as a list, which you can then cite easily.

uploading-references.en: Your reference(s) are getting added. Meanwhile, you can continue to edit your document. You will be notified here when the import is complete.

uploading-references-failure.en: Uploading references failed. We only support .bib and endnote xml format. Please, try again.

select-section-text.en: Below sections are suggested by the journal. Click to add
